      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Teerapong Tovirat</b>\n</p><p><b>Teerapong Tovirat</b>, \na Thai <a href=\"/FIDE\" title=\"FIDE\">FIDE</a> chess arbiter <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>, chess- and <a href=\"/index.php?title=Makruk&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Makruk (page does not exist)\">Thai chess</a> player <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, treasurer of the Thailand Chess Association <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>, and as <a href=\"/Checkers\" title=\"Checkers\">checkers</a> and chess programmer, author of the Thai Checkers <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> program <i>Turtle</i> and the <a href=\"/index.php?title=Makruk&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Makruk (page does not exist)\">Thai Chess</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> program <a href=\"/index.php?title=Jumbo_(Makruk)&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Jumbo (Makruk) (page does not exist)\">Jumbo</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Teerapong_Tovirat&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Teerapong_Tovirat&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=114311\">Question:1.hashtable 2.board 3.C</a> by Teerapong Tovirat, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 13, 2000&#160;» <a href=\"/Vector_Attacks\" title=\"Vector Attacks\">Vector Attacks</a>, <a href=\"/0x88\" title=\"0x88\">0x88</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=136488\">Fail-soft or Fail-hard&#160;?</a> by Teerapong Tovirat, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 04, 2000&#160;» <a href=\"/Fail-Soft\" title=\"Fail-Soft\">Fail-Soft</a>, <a href=\"/Fail-Hard\" title=\"Fail-Hard\">Fail-Hard</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=155677\">Bitboard VS array board, speed difference in movegen()</a> by Teerapong Tovirat, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 24, 2001&#160;» <a href=\"/Move_Generation\" title=\"Move Generation\">Move Generation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=182927\">\"Don't trust draw score\" &lt;=Is it true?</a> by Teerapong Tovirat, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 08, 2001&#160;» <a href=\"/Repetitions\" title=\"Repetitions\">Repetitions</a>, <a href=\"/Path-Dependency\" title=\"Path-Dependency\">Path-Dependency</a> </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=191460\">Re: A math problem for the experts...</a> by Teerapong Tovirat, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 02, 2001</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Teerapong_Tovirat&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=41575\">Parallel search, Where to start?</a>]by Teerapong Tovirat, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 24, 2011&#160;» <a href=\"/Parallel_Search\" title=\"Parallel Search\">Parallel Search</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=41892\">Iteration in pondering</a> by Teerapong Tovirat, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 09, 2012&#160;» <a href=\"/Pondering\" title=\"Pondering\">Pondering</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Teerapong_Tovirat&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ratings.fide.com/card.phtml?event=6200320\">Tovirat, Teerapong FIDE Chess Profile - Players Arbiters Trainers</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Teerapong_Tovirat&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ratings.fide.com/card.phtml?event=6200320\">Tovirat, Teerapong FIDE Chess Profile - Players Arbiters Trainers</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://bangkokchess.com/chess-ratings/thai-ratings\">Thai ratings | Bangkok Chess Club</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.fide.com/fide/directory.html?task=country&amp;fid=140\">FIDE Directory - Thailand Chess Association</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://mindsports.nl/index.php/on-the-evolution-of-draughts-variants/draughts-variants/500-thai\">Thai Checkers</a> from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://mindsports.nl/\">mindsports.nl</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Makruk\">Makruk from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://eng.thaibg.com/template.php?CenterFile=dw_all.php&amp;Title=Download\">Thai Board Games - Download</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301112326\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.011 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.011 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 107/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 234/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:111-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301112325 and revision id 7924\n -->\n"
